Module it.unipr.server

Package it.unipr.utilities

package it.unipr.utilities
This package contains the class Constants which provides to the software al its needed constant values.

Through this class all the packages of the software have access to an always up-to-date list of values that can be used whenever needed. For example, all the user interface messages are saved here.
